com.iciql

Class ValidationRemark

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iciql.ValidationRemark

  • public class ValidationRemark
extends java.lang.Object
    A validation remark is a result of running a model validation. Each remark has a level, associated component (schema, table, column, index), and a message.
